    <div class="card">
      <h2>Accessory Buildings & Structures</h2>
      <p>
        Accessory buildings and structures, except fences, shall maintain a minimum
        setback of <strong>5 feet from side and rear property lines</strong>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h2>Front Setback Notes</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Secondary front yard setbacks are <strong>15 feet</strong>.</li>
        <li>Cul-de-sac lots may reduce lot width at the building line by
            <strong>25 feet</strong>.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

